<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b14Mar1933"><font color="red">14 March 1933</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): I have written to Mr Morley asking for some corrections to be made in the event of a new printing of ALP and HCE but I will not bother you with these details as they can be done direct. </div>
